name: com.android.server.appsearch.contactsindexer.ContactsIndexerMaintenanceService
description: Generate job ids in the range (MIN_INDEXER_JOB_ID, MAX_INDEXER_JOB_ID) to avoid conflicts with other jobs scheduled by the system service. The range corresponds to 21475 job ids, which is the maximum number of user ids in the system. @see com.android.server.pm.UserManagerService#MAX_USER_ID
